    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个被毁灭的后末日世界中，你是一个精明的商人，从孤立的安全掩体中经营生意。你与外界的危险隔绝，依靠搜寻队进入荒芜的废土，寻找关键的补给品。每一次交易、每一笔生意都在塑造各个挣扎求生的派系之间脆弱的权力平衡，决定谁能繁荣，谁会衰亡。作为幸存者网络背后看不见的力量，你的商业决策不仅会决定你掩体的命运，还会影响掩体之外世界的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/4e5951fb0c82d96914afe0b019c768af.poster.avif?t=1770719087\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/4e5951fb0c82d96914afe0b019c768af.webm?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/4e5951fb0c82d96914afe0b019c768af.mp4?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >出售</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你扮演一个精明的商人角色，主要目标是尽可能多地出售商品，即使这可能损害与你交易的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/fda9c5de676cd5d7d45994d798e2a478.poster.avif?t=1770719087\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/fda9c5de676cd5d7d45994d798e2a478.webm?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/fda9c5de676cd5d7d45994d798e2a478.mp4?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >购买</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >派遣搜寻队前往战略位置，寻找有价值的物品；他们不一定每次都能活着回来，也不一定带回你所需要的东西，但只要你自己安全，这一切都是可以接受的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/6e3a7447ca8b3e1e0f6f2069a7598570.poster.avif?t=1770719087\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/6e3a7447ca8b3e1e0f6f2069a7598570.webm?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/6e3a7447ca8b3e1e0f6f2069a7598570.mp4?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩建掩体</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩建你的掩体，以容纳更多、更有价值的物品，并加强其安全性。记住，今天与你交易的人，明天可能会觊觎你的财产。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/36976f6dd4d2c7654c204bfb18211345.poster.avif?t=1770719087\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/36976f6dd4d2c7654c204bfb18211345.webm?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/36976f6dd4d2c7654c204bfb18211345.mp4?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >派系</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在交战的派系之间维持微妙的平衡；虽然他们常常用你的武器彼此厮杀，但如果某一方取得胜利，他们可能就不再需要你的服务了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/843d393937bd2eb8cd882fa3e879c534.poster.avif?t=1770719087\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/843d393937bd2eb8cd882fa3e879c534.webm?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033420/extras/843d393937bd2eb8cd882fa3e879c534.mp4?t=1770719087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的掩体是用混凝土建造的，但你不是。你需要抵御来自外部物品的辐射，并利用一切资源来应对因孤立而带来的压力，努力生存下去。</p>",
